{"title":"两台linux服务器配置远程免密登陆","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.041Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/两台linux服务器配置远程免密登陆","updated":"2023-07-28T09:22:02.416Z","content":"<p>@<a href=\"linux%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%99%BB%E9%99%86\">TOC</a><br>\n1、首先在<code>本机</code>和<code>远程机器</code>下执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>期间可以简单的直接按回车，下一步即可，生成机器的公私钥<br>\n2、查看<code>本机</code>的<code>id_rsa.pub</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、在远程机上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在其中贴入第二步查到的id_rsa.pub中的内容<br>\n然后按<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>，保存<br>\n4、修改其权限</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>5、然后在本机中执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh -l $&#123;登陆的用户名&#125; -p $&#123;远程登陆的端口&#125; $&#123;远程主机的ip&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>即可登陆。</p>\n<p>如果你很不幸出现了<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/131703405?spm=1001.2014.3001.5502\" target=\"_blank\">ssh_exchange_identification: read: Connection reset by peer</a>这个错误，可以参考我的<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/131703405?spm=1001.2014.3001.5502\" target=\"_blank\">另一篇文章</a>解决。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"腾讯云无法使用root登陆服务器","link":"2023/07/28/腾讯云无法使用root登陆服务器"},"next":{"title":"如何阻止gradle项目每次都自动下载依赖包到C盘","link":"2023/07/28/如何阻止gradle项目每次都自动下载依赖包到C盘"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/两台linux服务器配置远程免密登陆/","reading_time":"171 字约 1 分钟"}